&lt;p&gt;The right person for this role thrives in both the strategic and tactical – presenting quality trends and risks to executive leadership while rolling up their sleeves to drive improvement initiatives from insight to implementation understanding what “good” looks like and how to build the systems, tools, and team to get there.&lt;/p&gt;
