&lt;li&gt;Conduct structured root cause analysis on critical failures, escalations, and member complaint trends&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build business cases for improvement initiatives with clear ROI projections and measurable impact&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Pilot and test new processes, workflows, and member interaction scripts before scaling; create and maintain SOPs and documentation standards&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
